<a name="#main"><h1>Lennon Killer Chapman Denied Parole</h1></a>
<div class="attrib">
Written by <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20090427152540/http://blogcritics.org/writer/eric_olsen">Eric Olsen</a><br/>
Published October 09, 2002</div>
<div id="ad6"><!-- BEGIN STANDARD TAG - 300 x 250 - BlogCritics.org: Music - DO NOT MODIFY -->
