<div class="comment"><div class="cheader"><nobr><a name="comment-625616">#3</a> &mdash; August 26, 2007 @ 19:30PM &mdash; <b>Cristina</b></nobr></div><div class="cbody"><p>It's a good article.  Only that I cannot agree that John was "the" essence of The Beatles.  Johna and Paul were.  I think that John played off of Paul as much as the other way around.<br/>
